entries.journal_entry_description: Darth Vader congratulated you on your success.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Darth Vader] Captain Piett has reported that you have been successful in your mission. Your dedication to this matter has earned you additional rewards. I look forward to doing business in the future.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Cale Herron] I just heard someone successfully infiltrated the quarantine zone for the Empire. Whoever it was must have a great story.
